<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=5.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0f1419">
    <title>How to Play - Polynumba</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/polunumba_logo.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/auth.css">
    <style>
        .how-to-play-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .page-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
            padding-bottom: 24px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .page-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .page-header p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .content-section {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .content-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .content-section h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            margin-top: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .content-section p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .content-section ul, .content-section ol {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-left: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .content-section li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .game-type-card {
            background: var(--bg-secondary);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .game-type-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .game-type-header h4 {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .odds-badge {
            background: var(--accent-green);
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        .game-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .detail-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .detail-value {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .example-box {
            background: var(--bg-input);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-gold);
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .example-box strong {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .warning-box {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-red);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .warning-box h3 {
            color: var(--accent-red);
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .warning-box p {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .warning-box ul {
            margin-left: 24px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .warning-box li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-blue);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .info-box strong {
            color: var(--accent-blue);
        }

        .step-number {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            color: var(--bg-primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-right: 12px;
        }

        .back-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: var(--accent-red);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background 0.2s;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            background: #c1121f;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .how-to-play-container {
                padding: 24px 16px;
            }

            .page-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .content-section {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .game-details {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="how-to-play-container">
        <div class="page-header">
            <h1>How to Play Polynumba</h1>
            <p>Master the game and increase your chances of winning</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Game Overview -->
        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Game Overview</h2>
            <p>
                Polynumba is a number prediction game where players attempt to guess a sequence of randomly generated numbers. 
                The game offers two exciting modes: 4-Number Prediction and 3-Number Prediction. Each mode has its own payout 
                multiplier and number of attempts, giving you the flexibility to choose your preferred risk-reward ratio.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Game Modes -->
        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Game Modes & Customization</h2>
            
            <h3>Choose Your Number Type</h3>
            <div class="game-type-card">
                <div class="game-type-header">
                    <h4>4-Number Prediction</h4>
                </div>
                <p>Predict all 4 numbers in the correct sequence. More challenging but flexible attempts.</p>
                <div class="game-details">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Numbers</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">4 Numbers</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Number Range</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">0 - 9</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Unique Numbers</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">No Duplicates</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="game-type-card">
                <div class="game-type-header">
                    <h4>3-Number Prediction</h4>
                </div>
                <p>Predict all 3 numbers in the correct sequence. Simpler with flexible attempts.</p>
                <div class="game-details">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Numbers</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">3 Numbers</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Number Range</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">0 - 9</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Unique Numbers</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">No Duplicates</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>Choose Your Risk Level (Attempts & Odds)</h3>
            <p>
                You control the risk-reward ratio! Select how many attempts you want, and the odds adjust automatically. 
                Fewer attempts mean higher payouts, more attempts mean lower payouts but better chances to win.
            </p>

            <div class="game-type-card" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.05);">
                <h4 style="color: var(--accent-gold); margin-bottom: 16px;">Attempts & Odds Table</h4>
                <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <thead>
                        <tr style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);">
                            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; color: var(--text-secondary);">Attempts</th>
                            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; color: var(--text-secondary);">Odds</th>
                            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; color: var(--text-secondary);">Risk Level</th>
                            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; color: var(--text-secondary);">Example Win (₦1,000 bet)</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">2 Tries</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: 700;">10x</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--accent-red);">Very High Risk</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--text-primary);">₦10,000</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">3 Tries</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: 700;">8x</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: #f59e0b;">High Risk</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--text-primary);">₦8,000</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">4 Tries</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: 700;">6x</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: #3b82f6;">Medium Risk</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--text-primary);">₦6,000</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">5 Tries</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: 700;">4x</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: #10b981;">Low Risk</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--text-primary);">₦4,000</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600;">6 Tries</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: 700;">3x</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: #10b981;">Very Low Risk</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; color: var(--text-primary);">₦3,000</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- How to Play -->
        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>How to Play</h2>
            
            <h3><span class="step-number">1</span>Select Your Game Type</h3>
            <p>
                Choose between 4-Number Prediction or 3-Number Prediction. Both modes work the same way, 
                but 4-Number is more challenging as you need to predict more digits correctly.
            </p>

            <h3><span class="step-number">2</span>Choose Your Attempts (Risk Level)</h3>
            <p>
                Select how many attempts you want (2-6 tries). This is where you control your risk:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Fewer attempts (2-3):</strong> Higher odds (8x-10x) but harder to win</li>
                <li><strong>More attempts (5-6):</strong> Lower odds (3x-4x) but easier to win</li>
                <li><strong>Medium attempts (4):</strong> Balanced risk/reward at 6x odds</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                <strong>Important:</strong> Once you start the game, you cannot change the number of attempts!
            </p>

            <h3><span class="step-number">3</span>Place Your Bet</h3>
            <p>
                Enter the amount you wish to bet. Your bet amount will be deducted from your account balance 
                when you start the game. You can choose from preset amounts or enter a custom amount within your balance limit.
            </p>

            <h3><span class="step-number">4</span>Start the Game</h3>
            <p>
                Click the "Start Game" button. The system will generate a random sequence of numbers that you need to predict. 
                These numbers are generated on our secure server and cannot be manipulated.
            </p>

            <h3><span class="step-number">5</span>Make Your Prediction</h3>
            <p>
                Enter your predicted numbers in the correct sequence. Each position matters - the numbers must match 
                both in value and position to win. After entering your prediction, click the "Check" button to submit.
            </p>

            <h3><span class="step-number">6</span>Review Feedback</h3>
            <p>
                After each attempt, you'll receive feedback showing:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Correct Positions:</strong> Numbers that match both the value and position</li>
                <li><strong>Correct Numbers:</strong> Numbers that are correct but in the wrong position</li>
                <li><strong>Remaining Attempts:</strong> How many tries you have left</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="example-box">
                <strong>Example:</strong> If the winning numbers are [2, 5, 7, 9] and you guess [2, 3, 9, 7]:
                <ul style="margin-top: 8px;">
                    <li>Correct Positions: 1 (the number 2 is in the correct first position)</li>
                    <li>Correct Numbers: 2 (the numbers 7 and 9 are present but in wrong positions)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3><span class="step-number">7</span>Win or Try Again</h3>
            <p>
                If you predict all numbers correctly in their exact positions, you win! Your winnings will be 
                automatically credited to your account balance. If not, you can use your remaining attempts 
                to adjust your prediction based on the feedback provided.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Important Rules -->
        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Important Rules</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>All numbers are generated randomly using a secure algorithm, ensuring fair play.</li>
                <li>Generated numbers are unique - no number appears twice in the same sequence.</li>
                <li>You must predict the exact sequence - order matters for winning.</li>
                <li>Your bet amount is deducted when you start the game, not when you win or lose.</li>
                <li><strong>Once a game starts, you cannot change the number of attempts or odds.</strong></li>
                <li>Once a game starts, you cannot cancel or modify your bet amount.</li>
                <li>You must use all your attempts or win before you can start a new game.</li>
                <li>Winnings include your original bet amount PLUS your winnings (e.g., ₦1,000 bet at 8x = ₦8,000 winnings + ₦1,000 bet returned = ₦9,000 total).</li>
                <li>All game results are final and cannot be disputed once confirmed.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Winning Calculation -->
        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Winning Calculation</h2>
            <p>Your total payout is calculated based on your bet amount and the odds you selected:</p>
            
            <h3>Payout Formula</h3>
            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Total Payout = (Bet Amount × Odds) + Bet Amount</strong>
                <br><br>
                You get your winnings PLUS your original bet back!
            </div>

            <h3>Examples:</h3>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Scenario 1:</strong> ₦1,000 bet with 8x odds (3 attempts)
                <br>
                • Winnings: ₦1,000 × 8 = ₦8,000
                <br>
                • Bet returned: ₦1,000
                <br>
                • <strong>Total payout: ₦9,000</strong>
                <br>
                • Net profit: ₦8,000
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Scenario 2:</strong> ₦5,000 bet with 10x odds (2 attempts)
                <br>
                • Winnings: ₦5,000 × 10 = ₦50,000
                <br>
                • Bet returned: ₦5,000
                <br>
                • <strong>Total payout: ₦55,000</strong>
                <br>
                • Net profit: ₦50,000
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Scenario 3:</strong> ₦2,000 bet with 3x odds (6 attempts)
                <br>
                • Winnings: ₦2,000 × 3 = ₦6,000
                <br>
                • Bet returned: ₦2,000
                <br>
                • <strong>Total payout: ₦8,000</strong>
                <br>
                • Net profit: ₦6,000
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <strong>Remember:</strong> Your balance shows the total payout (winnings + bet returned), 
                so you always get your original bet back when you win!
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tips for Success -->
        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Tips for Success</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Try Practice Mode First:</strong> Use the Practice Mode to learn the game mechanics without risking real money.</li>
                <li><strong>Start Small:</strong> Begin with smaller bets while learning the game.</li>
                <li><strong>Choose Your Risk Level:</strong> More attempts = safer but lower payout. Fewer attempts = riskier but higher payout.</li>
                <li><strong>Use Feedback Wisely:</strong> Pay close attention to the feedback after each attempt to narrow down your next guess.</li>
                <li><strong>Manage Your Bankroll:</strong> Set a budget for your gaming session and stick to it.</li>
                <li><strong>Balance Risk & Reward:</strong> 4 attempts with 6x odds offers a good balance for most players.</li>
                <li><strong>Stay Patient:</strong> Take your time with each prediction - there's no time limit on your attempts.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Responsible Gaming -->
        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Responsible Gaming</h2>
            <p>
                Polynumba is designed for entertainment purposes. Please play responsibly and within your means. 
                If you feel that gaming is becoming a problem, please seek help or consider taking a break from the platform.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Only play with money you can afford to lose</li>
                <li>Set time and spending limits for yourself</li>
                <li>Take regular breaks during gaming sessions</li>
                <li>Never chase your losses</li>
                <li>Gaming should be fun, not a source of stress</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Terms and Disclaimer -->
        <div class="warning-box">
            <h3>⚠️ Important Disclaimer</h3>
            <p>
                Polynumba reserves the right to withhold winnings and suspend or terminate accounts if we detect 
                any malicious activities, fraudulent behavior, exploitation of system vulnerabilities, or violation 
                of our terms of service. This includes but is not limited to:
            </p>
            <ul style="margin-top: 16px; color: var(--text-primary);">
                <li>Use of automated bots or scripts</li>
                <li>Manipulation or exploitation of game mechanics</li>
                <li>Collusion with other players</li>
                <li>Multiple account creation to exploit bonuses</li>
                <li>Any form of cheating or unfair advantage</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 16px;">
                Additionally, we reserve the right to cancel games and refund bet amounts in cases where technical 
                errors or mistakes on our end may have affected game integrity or fairness. All decisions made by 
                Polynumba management regarding game outcomes and account status are final.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 16px; font-weight: 600;">
                By playing on Polynumba, you acknowledge and agree to these terms and conditions.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Need Help?</h2>
            <p>
                If you have any questions about how to play or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact 
                our support team. We're here to help ensure you have the best gaming experience possible.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="/" class="back-button">Back to Game</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

